{"tid":2385298,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男生被控雷射筆照警 陳炳宙裁定罪成 還押下月判刑","createTime":"2021-01-29T03:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T13:04:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a8ec75917c059f5df6abdf4b6d6010d39fe7f3","tid":2385298,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13308\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13308&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w3JTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=9358d841\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13308</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第五庭<br />\n#陳炳宙裁判官<br />\n#裁決 #20200119大埔<br />\n<br />\n吳 (17) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 在公眾地方管有 #攻擊性武器<br />\n2020年1月19日於大埔公路元洲仔段廣福邨行人天橋管有一支雷射筆<br />\n(2) #襲警 襲擊警務人員<br />\n廣福邨行人天橋襲擊高級警員PC47958<br />\n<br />\n❌不認罪❌<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n判詞稍後補回。<br />\n<br />\n速報<br />\n法庭宣布兩項控罪罪成‼️‼️<br />\n為被告索取勞教中心、更生中心報告。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2月19日930於粉嶺裁判法院第五庭判刑，期間被告還押‼️"},{"pid":"4b4d75810895d0f1244c3111d17488a39f34c426","tid":2385298,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32a582e95bdb8e6b0dd86ce2b600bfd9863c6ef","tid":2385298,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1ed51d39db5174de814c8d8c89e8a3924ada89","tid":2385298,"uid":31371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:34:57.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"174e506cf7153617cc5754f93140a7e87cb9e27f","tid":2385298,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1ddcb739b69a8c65b2aae4086677b7cc20bd95","tid":2385298,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"裁判官陳炳宙今裁決指，雖然受襲警員的證供前後不一致，且有誇大傷勢之嫌，但被告在警誡下承認曾用雷射筆照射警員，其行為必然是蓄意。雖然涉案雷射筆的射程不足以傷人，但這只反映被告愚蠢，使用了不適合的工具、在不適合的距離傷害警察，不影響襲警意圖，最終裁定襲警及管有雷射筆兩罪成立，還柙至下月19日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n就算手足自認照射黑警, 但唔一定算係攻擊<br />\n加上佢自己都話黑警證供有問題, 咁都得?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210129/SS2E7QP645EDDLJXHV3A7MEAWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210129%2FSS2E7QP645EDDLJXHV3A7MEAWE%2F&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w3JTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=0f0d2ad8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210129%2FSS2E7QP645EDDLJXHV3A7MEAWE%2F&h=bf0fc3d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210129/SS2E7QP645EDDLJXHV3A7MEAWE/</a>"},{"pid":"45f75318817fb3f97849a728b721e415ef0a2218","tid":2385298,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3353a